name: 1DLE/H4NDS
description:
There's been a hushed-up incident at the Naiman Cybernetics factory in Bigmosse. The corpos are sweating and they need it cleaned up- fast and off-the-books. Head in and clean house, but stay on your guard: this is just the tip of the iceberg.

A mission for CY_BORG. Comes in Classic yellow, Clean white and Nite grey.
